des:
Test your knowledge of your Favorite t. v. series quiz

t. v. Drama Quiz provides a fun way to play game with family and Friends and test your knowledge about the TV series

To start, just say "Alexa, start Quiz" or "Alexa, start game" to start the game".

At anytime, you can stop the game by saying "Alexa, stop"
